# Storybook Component Testing - Master Orchestrator

## Purpose

This is the **ENTRY POINT** for all Storybook component testing workflows for the **Modus Web Components 2.0** library. This file:
- Defines project context (Stencil web components, npm, Wireit)
- Routes commands to appropriate workflow files
- Enforces safety rules and boundaries
- Provides response templates

**All detailed workflows are in separate files for better maintainability.**

