## Step 1: Project State Detection

```typescript
// Check 1: Does .storybook/ exist?
const hasStorybook = true; // Already configured

// Check 2: Does playwright.config.ts exist?
const hasPlaywright = exists('playwright.config.ts');

// Check 3: Do .stories.ts files exist?
const storiesFiles = glob('src/components/**/*.stories.ts');
const hasStories = storiesFiles.length > 0; // 44 files exist

// Check 4: Do stories have play functions?
const hasPlayFunctions = storiesHavePlayFunctions(storiesFiles);
```

### State Matrix & Routing

| State | Setup | Stories | Play Functions | Route To |
|-------|-------|---------|----------------|----------|
| **Current State** | ✅ | ✅ (44) | ❌ | **→ File 0a** (Install Playwright deps) then **→ File 0b** (Add play functions) |
| **After Setup** | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | **→ File 0b** (Add Single Component) |
| **Tests Exist** | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | **→ File 0c** (Fix/Update) or **0d** (Remove) |

