## Command Reference

### Testing with Auto-Reports (PREFERRED)
```bash
# Single component — tests + auto-generates all 3 reports
npm run test:storybook:report -- Accordion

# All components — tests + auto-generates all 3 reports
npm run test:storybook:report:all
```

### Testing Only (no reports)
```bash
# Start Storybook dev server
npm run storybook:start

# Run interaction tests (Chromium only)
npm run test:storybook

# All browsers
npm run test:storybook:all

# Update snapshots
npm run test:storybook:update
```

### Unit Test Commands (existing)
```bash
npm test
npm run test:coverage
npm run test:update-snapshot
```

